<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero-small">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About CareerPath</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-card">
          <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            CareerPath is a career counseling platform designed to empower students from underserved communities in Hyderabad, Hajipur, and Kolkata. We combine scientifically structured psychometric assessments with expert human guidance to help students from 10th standard through graduation discover meaningful career paths.
          </p>

          <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-item">
              <h3>Our Mission</h3>
              <p>To provide accessible, trustworthy career guidance to students who lack traditional counseling resources. We believe every student deserves clarity about their future, regardless of their socioeconomic background.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-item">
              <h3>Grassroots Impact</h3>
              <p>We work directly with community organizations and educational institutions in slum-adjacent areas, delivering assessments in simple English and connecting students with counselors who understand local employment landscapes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-item">
              <h3>Our Approach</h3>
              <p>Students complete a comprehensive 50-question assessment covering aptitude, personality, interests, emotional intelligence, and skills. Results generate rule-based career recommendations matched to specialized counselors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-item">
              <h3>Our Vision</h3>
              <p>To become the most trusted career guidance platform for first-generation learners in Eastern and Southern India, expanding access to vocational training, higher education, and sustainable employment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
